channel.description:

A good example of what I was listening to is "DJ Quicksilver - BitterSweet Symphony". That's is the only I could think of, or had listened to before.
I would be really greatful if someone could give me the genre of music that is, or give me a song list of all the "transformed" symphonies.
Much love
